('foundation', 'synonyms-antonyms', 'beginner', 'Choose the opposite of "love":', '["Hate", "Like", "Adore", "Cherish"]', 0, 'Antonym: Hate is the opposite of love - they represent opposite emotions. Like, adore, and cherish are similar to love.', 'medium'),
('foundation', 'synonyms-antonyms', 'beginner', 'Choose the opposite of "safe":', '["Dangerous", "Secure", "Protected", "Guarded"]', 0, 'Antonym: Dangerous is the opposite of safe - they represent opposite levels of risk. Secure, protected, and guarded are similar to safe.', 'medium'),
